{"tid":1473854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解D記者唔可以咁樣問問題？","createTime":"2019-08-15T03:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T16:10:18.000Z","uid":242278,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ca7aa4f5357110deaf9083df2a8b1a3b67db8e7a","tid":1473854,"uid":242278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:27:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你唔直接否認呢個問題，我會當你默認</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記者<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗<br />\n<br />\n舉個例<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：想問有冇警察假扮示威者混入群？如果你唔直接否認呢個問題，我會當你默認。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：err.....我哋有警員...errr...喬裝...err...成為唔同嘅人士...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁即係冇否認啦？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：err...errr...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完美二分法，答又死唔答又死，因為冇直接否認，等同唔俾班狗有詞語去修飾（咩叫任何人士啊、最佳使用日期啊之類），但佢話冇資料冇證據個D都仲係冇辦法。<br />\n<br />\n希望記者朋友見到可以用下呢個方法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外幫攬炒巴賣下廣告<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EgoGfQD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEgoGfQD.png&h=2f0beb5c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BK1TRoZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBK1TRoZ.png&h=6f868251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日收工後遮打花園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a290690ddfde32bd71c5eafdc44d2feaf3398d58","tid":1473854,"uid":242278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:27:48.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"729ec9a2067084fd3d0c98e35f